snippet.textDisplay: Plot Twist: Damien was Billy, who had adapted to his environment as an employee after being left there by his mother for years. After finally realizing that he was at the Ikea, the mother went to go find him. But after so much time, they don't recognize each other and the mother takes the shelf in a desperate attempt of denial to normalize life after the father had gone insane for having lost his child and the hands of his irresponsible wife.
